{"tid":1389406,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"RFID垃圾燈柱一問","createTime":"2019-07-31T01:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T17:08:50.000Z","uid":278102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"697795b90dc6f587759a25236ec452b5b7202310","tid":1389406,"uid":278102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:50:41.000Z","msg":"其實RFID係咪姐係好似加強咗既手機NFC功能咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係平時手機NFC都要靠到好近先拍到信用卡嗰啲嘢，係咪因為個垃圾燈柱夠大放到高功率既接受器先可以做到隔空讀取既功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ddf90f646a023db596959adfa8d8450491ed70","tid":1389406,"uid":278102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實RFID係咪姐係好似加強咗既手機NFC功能咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係平時手機NFC都要靠到好近先拍到信用卡嗰啲嘢，係咪因為個垃圾燈柱夠大放到高功率既接收器先可以做到隔空讀取既功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c632ac911b73dd3cb535d18232869812696981c5","tid":1389406,"uid":278102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:29:10.000Z","msg":"有無人答下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d71a60dc7b90e6c7c72a285fa5ce1bb1f1b169","tid":1389406,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:31:20.000Z","msg":"距離遠啲<br />\n<br />\n好似一間賣珠寶既舖頭 佢一撳就棈到全舖頭有邊件貨係到咁"},{"pid":"a2619f70dc77c87cf6ba075088d9480380cdcc2e","tid":1389406,"uid":6366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:37:11.000Z","msg":"Nfc係由rdif演化<br />\n你可以視nfc為 為左增加安全性/用於現金交易<br />\n所以縮短左讀取資料既距離<br />\n<br />\n印象中Rdif 被讀出一方甚至可以主動發出訊號 當然身份證唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a854a65e4fdde384c44c53dd0cfc3733dab011e3","tid":1389406,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"RFID 先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b79931ce7eb819f2f83d5ca78eeb8dcd7ea40d0","tid":1389406,"uid":278102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來係咁，我仲以為呢樣就係nfc既加強版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為我睇完隔離post話回鄉証有rfid，我拎張回鄉証拍落手機度又真係會彈舊嘢出嚟，身份証就無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce41d9f69a54760d8079ca6f2a0ddcac80d450eb","tid":1389406,"uid":278102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b79931ce7eb819f2f83d5ca78eeb8dcd7ea40d0","tid":1389406,"uid":278102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來係咁，我仲以為呢樣就係nfc既加強版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為我睇完隔離post話回鄉証有rfid，我拎張回鄉証拍落手機度又真係會彈舊嘢出嚟，身份証就無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:17:53.000Z","msg":"btw張回鄉証過咗期已經好耐，無咩事都唔想再申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca5bccd973eb84d4cbbd6e14b6d6989f5eba7ba","tid":1389406,"uid":266972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:08:50.000Z","msg":"根據2015年2月3日立法會保安事務委員會討論文件 - 建議新一代智能身份證系統 保安及私隱保障特徵的補充資料 <br />\n建議的新智能身份證將嚴格按照<span style=\"color: orange;\">ISO  14443（A或B型）</span>標準設計<br />\n<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr14-15/chinese/panels/se/papers/se20150203cb2-654-3-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr14-15%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fse%2Fpapers%2Fse20150203cb2-654-3-c.pdf&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij85RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=ee18240f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr14-15/chinese/panels/se/papers/se20150203cb2-654-3-c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nISO 14443為近距離非接觸式智慧卡(Proximity  Cards)，其感測距離為<span style=\"color: red;\">0~10公分</span>，屬於較普遍性的應用方式。由於操作條件適中，因此，為目前非接觸式智慧卡相關規範中最普遍、主流的應用。<span style=\"color: orange;\">e.g. VISA, MASTER Card</span><br />\n<br />\n但2013年曾有測試使用 ISO/IEC 14443 type A 實現了<span style=\"color: red;\">最大18米的竊聽距離</span><br />\nRef: <a href=\"http://rfid-handbook.de/downloads/Systech2013_eavesdropping_Engelhardt_Pfeiffer_Finkenzeller.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frfid-handbook.de%2Fdownloads%2FSystech2013_eavesdropping_Engelhardt_Pfeiffer_Finkenzeller.pdf&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij85RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=4f980820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rfid-handbook.de/downloads/Systech2013_eavesdropping_Engelhardt_Pfeiffer_Finkenzeller.pdf</a>"}]}